{"tid":429041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個講野唔算數既冇信用仆街","createTime":"2017-10-08T14:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T17:12:05.000Z","uid":152080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b83f99210e10e8e5dbb730c2eb616d37b6ac936d","tid":429041,"uid":152080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"小弟因為工作關系經常要約客戶出黎傾野<br />\n咁就成日會遇到D冇信用既仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明係電話到溝通左好耐 好多野都講好晒話想點做點做<br />\n之後我就<strong>提早成個星期約實時間</strong><br />\n但係到左預約時間就同我講&ldquo;sorry唔得閒,我地約過時間好嗎&rdquo;？<br />\n仆街D既就直接玩消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌呀，你知唔知我做左幾多準備功夫 晒左我幾多時間精力<br />\n我推撚晒其他工作<br />\n就係為左呢日出黎同你傾合作，而你就一撚D誠意都冇<br />\n搞到我浪費晒成個星期時間，同埋其他客戶<br />\n你唔係真係覺得仲會有合作機會掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16a25c6e1a3aeb06cd95c5b9f52c1f485eac20f","tid":429041,"uid":152080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"推～<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f815063d7f1a54d41028f505792dbc074592ac6d","tid":429041,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"咩工？"},{"pid":"12d7dc6cea395d084f6ba6981bd2d7dd124b705f","tid":429041,"uid":152080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩工？</blockquote><br />\n都係D搵唔到咩錢既工姐 不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw有冇故事分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b4f97d24409e89e09f4474da126837fb1dd42e","tid":429041,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩工？</blockquote><br />\n都係D搵唔到咩錢既工姐 不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /